visits by American representatives to Russia. European leaders urged a firmer stance against Moscow at the G7 summit.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/zelenskyy-can-always-come-to-moscow-russias-open-invitation-to-ukrainian-prez-for-serious-dialogue/articleshow/131779018.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/zelenskyy-can-always-come-to-moscow-russias-open-invitation-to-ukrainian-prez-for-serious-dialogue/articleshow/131779018.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-16T23:18:44+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131779092,imgsize-816970.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US used Iran-style covert transfers to move 90 million barrels of oil out of Gulf: Report]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131777105.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The U.S. has reportedly established a covert offshore oil-transfer network near the Strait of Hormuz, mirroring Iran's tactics to maintain Gulf crude exports. This operation, involving ship-to-ship transfers off Oman and the UAE, aims to circumvent Tehran's blockade of the vital waterway. While enabling continued exports, the network's reliance on clandestine methods raises concerns about its vulnerability and the U.S.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-used-iran-style-covert-transfers-to-move-90-million-barrels-of-oil-out-of-gulf-report/articleshow/131777105.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-used-iran-style-covert-transfers-to-move-90-million-barrels-of-oil-out-of-gulf-report/articleshow/131777105.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-16T22:19:36+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131777258,imgsize-614951.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Donald Trump's White House ballroom cost estimated at $600 million, taxpayers footing half the bill: Report]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131776674.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Trump's ambitious White House ballroom project is now reportedly costing a staggering $600 million, with over half expected to be funded by taxpayers, contradicting earlier claims of private financing. Despite assurances of a "tax-payer free" initiative, internal plans reveal significant public funds allocated to the construction, sparking controversy and legal challenges.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-white-house-ballroom-cost-estimated-at-600-million-taxpayers-footing-half-the-bill-report/articleshow/131776674.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-white-house-ballroom-cost-estimated-at-600-million-taxpayers-footing-half-the-bill-report/articleshow/131776674.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-16T21:59:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131776954,imgsize-947838.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[How tall is Vice President JD Vance? His reply to surprised hosts of 'The View' as he walks in the studio]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131776803.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/how-tall-is-vice-president-jd-vance-his-reply-to-surprised-hosts-of-the-view-as-he-walks-in-the-studio/articleshow/131776803.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[htt